\n市民對法律失去信心佢地就收撚皮架啦"},{"pid":"345ddad11ec5d3c0c43b95335fa8afac61f5fad7","tid":374793,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"我諗三子係咪政治犯，市民同其他囚犯都心中有數<br />\n<br />\n犯法一定要坐監？罰錢，仲有社會服務令呢？"},{"pid":"212215ad04196f8d8a363446cc52dedec2ef2173","tid":374793,"uid":51455,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"其實仲相信香港有司法獨立真係好天真，經過廿年，好多嘢已經俾中共搞掂咗"},{"pid":"b0ed322d327dec67c90f57bc02d8cb7f6d7925b2","tid":374793,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"７７７原本諗住搵佢做律政屍，佢咁既答覆一啲都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53811b498dbeda305cd2b077c985f0975b3e7371","tid":374793,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你會發現好多大律師同大法官 好多港大學者本身都唔係奶共 自從淋病上任之後就奶曬共<br />\n淋病真係可以做到食左你地都唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有咩證明佢奶共?<br />\n你冇任何野理據,單憑人地唔支持黃之鋒督話人奶共<br />\n<br />\n其他你同大陸D憤青有乜鳩分別,少少理性討論都唔識<br />\n<br />\n咁撚支持黃之鋒你去劫獄呀笨,橫掂你都唔覺黃有錯,支持你呀,唔好上網啦</blockquote><br />\n嗯 閱"},{"pid":"48f71edb17a3dd10b0186ef0196730c1010ac8c0","tid":374793,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>７７７原本諗住搵佢做律政屍，佢咁既答覆一啲都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e336e6358e2b9542b867dbbc804e5f1c4c86e7","tid":374793,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>７７７原本諗住搵佢做律政屍，佢咁既答覆一啲都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要說服呀爺比佢做下任"}]}